column5: Hey OFC'ers,  I'm looking for another I.T. Related Position. This is due to the travel time it takes me to get to work (approx. 1hr). If anyone out there are I.T. Recruiters, I can send a resume upon request. My apologies if I've posted this in the wrong area.  Thanks, A2F (Rob)
I can check our civilian postings to see if there's anything for I.t
